battle_skill_config-280300301:
Upon Damage Focus N's activation, if the enemy with the highest HP is an armored unit, launch missiles to deal 0.6x damage against the target and 0.2x damage (affected by armor) to enemies within a radius of 2.
If the enemy with the highest HP is not an armored unit, throw a cluster grenade to deal 0.2x damage 7 times to enemies within a radius of 1 yard. Enemies hit more than once will receive 50% reduced damage (can be evaded, affected by armor).
Furthermore, increase movement speed by 500% and normal attacks will pierce enemies with 1x damage. If there are enemies directly in front of her, switch to energy blade mode to deal 1x damage to those enemies.

The additional skill uses incur no aiming time and do not gain bonus DMG from charge stacks, dealing 3x DMG that can miss, depending on target's EVA. Prioritizes enemy with the lowest HP that can be killed in one shot.
Increase DMG of normal attacks and skill by 10% when attacking enemies with more than 50% HP.
